TACKLIN FUEL bumped foe at the start, then vied early before chasing the pace from the two path into the turn, bid while four wide heading into the lane but came up evenly. TREMOR was bumped at the start, then settled towards the back of the group with inner rivals, then made a mild bid while five wide on the turn and came up empty in the stretch. BOOMING vied for the lead early, then steadied heading into the turn, rebid along the inside in the early stretch and needed more in the end. HOLIDAY CITY was bumped by rival at the start then settled along the inside and was no rally. GLAZED was bumped at the start then trailed behind the field and was no factor.
